Titolo: Blades of Thunder II

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Blades of Thunder 2, also sold as Battle Hawks 2, is a flight simulator game developed by Interactive Visison A/S's Polish studio and published by Summitsoft Entertainment for the Nintendo DS. It was released on April 18, 2006 in North America. It received poor reviews, with GameSpot saying that "There's nothing fun or exciting about flying helicopters in Blades of Thunder II. And considering that's all you do in the game, that's really sad."